8250_tegra: clean up tegra_uart_handle_break

* switch "do { A; } while (1)" to "while (1) { A; }"
* switch "if (A) B; else break;" to "if (!A) break; B;"
* remove unused assignment from p->serial_in() to status

Objdump -d shows no difference.

